casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Christine A. AGOLA.
No. D-2914.
Supreme Court of the United States
July 18, 2016.
Christine A. Agola, of Rochester, New York, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
